*
******************************************************************************
*  Model performance : 
*  - Static Electrical Characteristics and Dynamic Electrical Characteristics 
*    are modeled with the typical values from the datasheet.
*  - Temperature effects are not modeled
*
*  The following features have been modeled :
*  - Switching Characteristics such as propagation delay
*  - Undervoltage lockout
*  - Programmable fault clear time
*  - Over-current detection with positive voltage input
*
******************************************************************************
* PINS:  
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  | 	 NAME 	| DESCRIPTION                                           
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |	 GND1 	| Ground Primary Side
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  | 	 VCC1 	| Primary Power Supply
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     DATA 	| ADC/DIAG Data Output (push-pull)
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     NFLT   | Fault Output (open-drain, low active)
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     RDY  	| Ready Output (open-drain, low active)
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     NRST 	| Reset Input (rising-edge)
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     EN     | Enable Input (high active)
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     INN 	| Negative PWM Input (Monitoring Input)
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     INP    | Positive PWM Input
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     GND1 	| Ground Primary Side
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  | GATE/CLAMP | Gate Monitoring Input/ Miller Clamp Output
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     TOUT   | Transistor Output
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     VCC2   | Secondary Positive Power Supply 
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     DESAT  | Desaturation Protection Input
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     GND2   | Ground Secondary Side
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     ASC    | ASC Input  
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     OCPP   | Over Current Protection Input Positive
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     OCPN   | Over Current Protection Input Negative
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  |     VEE2 	| Secondary Negative Power Supply
*  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
*
******************************************************************************
